Besides the permanent shops we have a market in the area. This market is held on Thursday and Saturday each week.The market is situated in{Church Street,}the main shopping street of{Abertillery.}
The market is of a general kind with produce,clothing,household and domestic goods predominating.Many of the stallholders travel around the markets{Gwent}on a regular route:_ {Abergavenny Tuesdays,Pontypridd {Wednesdays and Abertillery Thursdays.
The market attracts people from the whole of the Abertillery district and the surrounding area.This is a welcome boost to the local shops usual trade but does cause some traders concern if they have a specialist commodity that is in competition with a market stall.
